==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Maltonic
<hw>Mal*ton"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or derived from, maltose; specif., designating
an acid called also <altname>gluconic</altname> or
<altname>dextronic</altname> acid. See <er>Gluconic</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Maltose</ent>⟦br⟧
